(500, '_transient_nimble_api_posts', 'a:3:{s:9:\"timestamp\";i:1631101032;s:9:\"start_msg\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"latest_posts\";a:4:{i:0;a:4:{s:5:\"title\";s:50:\"⚡️ Nimble Builder Pro introduces masonry grids\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:350:\"The latest version of Nimble Builder Pro introduces a new masonry grid set of options to the Post Grid module. This new features allows the creation of truly beautiful grids, and let users control everything : number of columns by devices or fixed column width, space between columns and rows, padding, rounded corners, shadow, background, [&hellip;]\";s:7:\"created\";s:19:\"2021-07-12 16:40:32\";s:3:\"url\";s:71:\"https://presscustomizr.com/nimble-builder-pro-introduces-masonry-grids/\";}i:1;a:4:{s:5:\"title\";s:97:\"Nimble Builder adds clone feature to multi-items module like carousel, accordion and social links\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:349:\"The latest version of Nimble Builder introduces a clone icon next to the items in module like slider or accordion. All properties of the cloned items are copied, which greatly speeds up the design experience. Recently introduced Starter template picker This new features allows you to pick pre-built templates, and save and reuse your own [&hellip;]\";s:7:\"created\";s:19:\"2021-06-25 15:12:48\";s:3:\"url\";s:124:\"https://presscustomizr.com/nimble-builder-adds-clone-feature-to-multi-items-module-like-carousel-accordion-and-social-links/\";}i:2;a:4:{s:5:\"title\";s:55:\"Nimble Builder received an awesome review today !☺️\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:314:\"One of the best plugins and theme/page builders I have ever used. Thank you so much for this amazing piece of software. And personally I would like to thanks to the development team for the support they are providing as they always respond back to bugs and feature requests. keep up your good work; long [&hellip;]\";s:7:\"created\";s:19:\"2021-06-25 00:05:43\";s:3:\"url\";s:94:\"https://presscustomizr.com/nimble-builder-received-an-awesome-review-today-%e2%98%ba%ef%b8%8f/\";}i:3;a:4:{s:5:\"title\";s:47:\"⚡️ Nimble Builder introduces site templates\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:340:\"Nimble Builder introduces a site building feature allowing you to define site wide templates for all contexts of your WordPress site. Nimble Builder includes a library of starter templates but you can create and use your own templates. For example, you can define a 2 columns template for all your pages, and use dynamic template [&hellip;]\";s:7:\"created\";s:19:\"2021-04-25 18:16:27\";s:3:\"url\";s:68:\"https://presscustomizr.com/nimble-builder-introduces-site-templates/\";}}}', 'no'),
